Mac OSX vs Vagrant
# Big Picture
requests happen when human clicks a link/submits a form in browser
servers serve requests
navigate the browser to http://codeup.dev/hello_world.html
sending a request to that address for that resource
server listens for requests to that host
server figures out what to do
# Mac OS X       
file system
Chrome or any browser
Sublime Text
~/vagrant-lamp/sites/codeup.dev
~/vagrant-lamp/
ansible
Sequel Pro
# vagrant VM
virtualized Ubuntu linux install
web server (NGINX)
MySQL database
server logs
PHP - our server side programming language
/vagrant/sites/codeup.dev
composer
artisan
